Load .qs file from a remote connection

Source: R/from_url.R
qs_from_url.Rd

Load .qs file from a remote connection

qs_from_url(url)

Arguments

url

a character url

Value

a dataframe as parsed by qs::qdeserialize()

Examples

# \donttest{
qs_from_url(
"https://github.com/nflverse/nflfastR-data/raw/master/data/play_by_play_2020.qs"
)
